nset-0\"><img alt=\"Community gathering\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover opacity-20\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-community.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-community.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-community.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-community.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-community.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-community.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-community.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-community.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-community.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-dem-blue via-dem-blue/95 to-dem-blue-dark/90\"></div></div><div class=\"relative mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><h1 class=\"text-4xl font-extrabold text-white sm:text-5xl\">Who We Are</h1><p class=\"mt-4 text-xl text-white/80\">The Democratic Party of Mendocino County</p></div></section><section class=\"py-16 sm:py-20\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"relative mb-12 h-64 overflow-hidden rounded-xl sm:h-80\"><img alt=\"Mendocino County redwood forests\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fredwoods.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fredwoods.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fredwoods.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fredwoods.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fredwoods.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fredwoods.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fredwoods.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fredwoods.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fredwoods.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/30 to-transparent\"></div></div><div class=\"prose max-w-none\"><p>We are a group of people who share progressive democratic values. As a political party, we work to promote these ideals in Mendocino County through our elected officials and by encouraging political, social, and environmental issues that reflect our vision.</p>\n<h2>The Central Committee</h2>\n<p>The Mendocino County Democratic Central Committee (MCDP) is the official local arm of the California Democratic Party. Our committee is made up of elected and appointed members who are passionate about making a difference in our community.</p>\n<h2>What We Do</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Support Democratic Candidates:</strong> We endorse and support Democratic candidates running for local, state, and federal office in Mendocino County.</li>\n<li><strong>Voter Outreach:</strong> We register voters, provide information about candidates and ballot measures, and work to increase voter turnout.</li>\n<li><strong>Community Engagement:</strong> We host events, forums, and meetings to keep our community informed and engaged in the democratic process.</li>\n<li><strong>Advocacy:</strong> We advocate for policies that reflect our progressive values, from environmental protection to social justice.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Our History</h2>\n<p>The Mendocino County Democratic Central Committee has been serving our community for decades, working to ensure that the voices of Mendocino County residents are heard at every level of government. From the redwood forests to the rugged coastline, we represent the diverse communities that make up our beautiful county.</p>\n<h2>Central Committee Members</h2>\n<p>The committee is composed of elected and appointed Democrats from across Mendocino County who volunteer their time to strengthen our party and our community.</p>\n<p><strong>Officers:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Chair:</strong> <em>(Update via admin panel)</em></li>\n<li><strong>Vice Chair:</strong> <em>(Update via admin panel)</em></li>\n<li><strong>Secretary:</strong> <em>(Update via admin panel)</em></li>\n<li><strong>Treasurer:</strong> <em>(Update via admin panel)</em></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Committee Members:</strong>\r\n<em>(Committee members can be added and updated through the admin panel at /admin)</em></p>\n<p><em>If you are a registered Democrat interested in serving on the Central Committee, please contact us or attend one of our monthly meetings.</em></p>\n<h2>Monthly Meetings</h2>\n<p>We hold regular monthly meetings that are open to all registered Democrats. These meetings are an opportunity to hear from candidates, discuss issues affecting our community, and get involved in upcoming campaigns and events. Check our Events page for the next meeting date and location.</p>\n</div></div></section><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"bg-dem-blue-dark text-white\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 lg:py-16\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4\"><div class=\"lg:col-span-2\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-white\">Mendocino County Democratic Central Committee</h2><address class=\"mt-4 not-italic leading-relaxed text-white/70\"><p>PO Box 28</p><p>Ukiah, CA 95482</p></address><div class=\"mt-6 flex items-center gap-4\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Mendodems/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white/10 p-2.5 text-white transition-colors duration-200 hover:bg-white/20\" aria-label=\"Follow us on Facebook\"><svg class=\"h-5 w-5\" fill=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M22 12c0-5.523-