03c/h2\\u003e\\n\\u003cul\\u003e\\n\\u003cli\\u003e\\u003cstrong\\u003eSupport Democratic Candidates:\\u003c/strong\\u003e We endorse and support Democratic candidates running for local, state, and federal office in Mendocino County.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\n\\u003cli\\u003e\\u003cstrong\\u003eVoter Outreach:\\u003c/strong\\u003e We register voters, provide information about candidates and ballot measures, and work to increase voter turnout.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\n\\u003cli\\u003e\\u003cstrong\\u003eCommunity Engagement:\\u003c/strong\\u003e We host events, forums, and meetings to keep our community informed and engaged in the democratic process.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\n\\u003cli\\u003e\\u003cstrong\\u003eAdvocacy:\\u003c/strong\\u003e We advocate for policies that reflect our progressive values, from environmental protection to social justice.\\u003c/li\\u003e\\n\\u003c/ul\\u003e\\n\\u003ch2\\u003eOur History\\u003c/h2\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003eThe Mendocino County Democratic Central Committee has been serving our community for decades, working to ensure that the voices of Mendocino County residents are heard at every level of government. From the redwood forests to the rugged coastline, we represent the diverse communities that make up our beautiful county.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003ch2\\u003eCentral Committee Members\\u003c/h2\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003eThe committee is composed of elected and appointed Democrats from across Mendocino County who volunteer their time to strengthen our party and our community.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003e\\u003cstrong\\u003eOfficers:\\u003c/strong\\u003e\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003cul\\u003e\\n\\u003cli\\u003e\\u003cstrong\\u003eChair:\\u003c/strong\\u003e \\u003cem\\u003e(Update via admin panel)\\u003c/em\\u003e\\u003c/li\\u003e\\n\\u003cli\\u003e\\u003cstrong\\u003eVice Chair:\\u003c/strong\\u003e \\u003cem\\u003e(Update via admin panel)\\u003c/em\\u003e\\u003c/li\\u003e\\n\\u003cli\\u003e\\u003cstrong\\u003eSecretary:\\u003c/strong\\u003e \\u003cem\\u003e(Update via admin panel)\\u003c/em\\u003e\\u003c/li\\u003e\\n\\u003cli\\u003e\\u003cstrong\\u003eTreasurer:\\u003c/strong\\u003e \\u003cem\\u003e(Update via admin panel)\\u003c/em\\u003e\\u003c/li\\u003e\\n\\u003c/ul\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003e\\u003cstrong\\u003eCommittee Members:\\u003c/strong\\u003e\\r\\n\\u003cem\\u003e(Committee members can be added and updated through the admin panel at /admin)\\u003c/em\\u003e\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003e\\u003cem\\u003eIf you are a registered Democrat interested in serving on the Central Committee, please contact us or attend one of our monthly meetings.\\u003c/em\\u003e\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\\u003ch2\\u003eMonthly Meetings\\u003c/h2\\u003e\\n\\u003cp\\u003eWe hold regular monthly meetings that are open to all registered Democrats. These meetings are an opportunity to hear from candidates, discuss issues affecting our community, and get involved in upcoming campaigns and events. Check our Events page for the next meeting date and location.\\u003c/p\\u003e\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"10:[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"section\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"relative overflow-hidden bg-dem-blue py-16 sm:py-20\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"absolute inset-0\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L18\\\",null,{\\\"src\\\":\\\"/images/hero-community.jpg\\\",\\\"alt\\\":\\\"Community gathering\\\",\\\"fill\\\":true,\\\"className\\\":\\\"object-cover opacity-20\\\",\\\"priority\\\":true}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-dem-blue via-dem-blue/95 to-dem-blue-dark/90\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"relative mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h1\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-4xl font-extrabold text-white sm:text-5xl\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Who We Are\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mt-4 text-xl text-white/80\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\